body:
### Welcome to The Kruskamp Group.
We've been spending so much time with our projects we've not finished our site. It's the old plumber with leaky pipes analogy. We've started putting more focus on the site, and hopefully it will be out soon.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
